         <div type="abstract">
            <head>Abstract:</head>
            <p>Viktor IV. stellt das Kloster S. Martin de Glandières unter Abt Folmar unter seinen Schutz und bestätigt sämtliche Besitzungen.<list>
                  <item>[Listeneintrag 1]</item>
               </list></p>
         </div>

         <div>
            <head>Incipit:</head><diploPart type="incipit" xml:lang="lat">Apostolice sedis consuetudo deposcit et</diploPart>
         </div>
         <div>
            <head>Subscriptiones:</head>
            <diploPart type="subscriptio" xml:lang="lat"><list>
                  <item>[R] Ego <persName>Victor catholice ecclesie episcopus</persName> subscripsi. [BV]</item><item>Ego <persName>Liudo [episcopus</persName> subscripsi]. Ego <persName>Teodericus Signinus episcopus</persName> subscripsi. </item><item>Ego <persName>Guido presbiter cardinalis</persName> tituli Calixti subscripsi. Ego <persName>Hunfridus presbiter cardinalis</persName> tituli sancte Susanne subscripsi. Ego <persName>Albertus presbiter cardinalis</persName> tituli sancti Grisogoni subscripsi.</item><item>Ego <persName>Landus diaconus cardinalis</persName> sancti Angeli subscripsi. Ego <persName>Gerardus diaconus cardinalis</persName> sancte Marie in Aquiro subscripsi.</item>
               </list></diploPart>
         </div>
         <div>
            <head>Datatio:</head><diploPart type="datatio">Datum Cremone per manum Iohannis sancte Romane ecclesie presbiteri cardinalis et cancellarii, indictione XI incarnationis dominice anno MCLXIIII, pontificatus vero dompni Victoris pape IIII anno IIII.</diploPart>
